How setting my scripts folder

»Give executable permission in all scripts with:
	sudo chmod 777 file_name.sh

»Open .bashrc and insert

	SCRIPTS="$HOME/Scripts"
	export SCRIPTS

»Insert in /usr/local/bin: (ubuntu 20 is /bin)
	sudo ln -s $SCRIPTS/kill.sh my_kill

»Insert a keyboard shortcut
	 bind -x '"\C-k":my_kill'

»Insert the following command in "Startup applications" (in app menu)
	sh /home/joaopedro/Scripts/my_init_script
